Tigerhawk races through the alliance finds his exit and makes a quick escape 
and heads towards the maximal base

::Elsewhere::

Liono looks back over his shoulder "Where is Dark?"  As he jets over the 
water. 

Dark laughing harshly "right above you little brother" As Dark cups his hands 
and hammers Liono in his back. 

Liono shoots into the water slowly he swims under dark and switches his jets 
to silent running.

Dark flies around in a circle "he will surface soon."

Liono watches dark circle "Jets maximum burn." Liono shoots out the water 
jumping on Darks back putting a dark in a neck Lock aiming him at a mountain.

Dark spirals towards the mountain out of control "What in the hell?"  

Liono jumps off guide missile lock fire Liono fires 4 missiles in darks 
direction 

Dark Flies into the mountains side and then it explodes with the missile fire.
"AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAARRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRGGGGGGGGGHHHHHHHHHHH"
Dark stands up slowly and takes off at extremely high speed rushing at 
Liono's back side.

Liono turns around looking at dark "This is going to the hurt."

Dark backhands Liono with all his might. 

Liono get knocked back rolling several feet landing on his back.

Dark Jumps in to the air landing on Liono chest "Now you will sing for me 
little birdie."
As Dark puts one foot on his chest and slowly starts to at pressure.

Liono chest plate starts to dent under the pressure.

Dark looking down at him "Where are you friends now? Or the Woman you fight 
to protect? Your weak?" As he Adds a little more pressure.

Liono eyes struggles open to stay online drifting on the brink of going 
offline."AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA"
